{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362620/extras/rv-gif-5.gif?t=1727954263\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your dream RV! Find classic, unique campers, busses, minivans or caravans. Restore them, give them a new look and bring them back to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362620/extras/rv-gif-7.gif?t=1727954263\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Visit Junkyard to find old or destroyed Recreational Vehicles and bring them back to life. Repair them in your workshop and give them a new look. Pimp your ride!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362620/extras/rv-gif-2-1-1.gif?t=1727954263\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remove the rust, repair the engine, change tires or seats or make an extreme rebuild of your RV. Choose if you want to make the repairs yourself or delegate them to a professional mechanic. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362620/extras/rv-gif-3.gif?t=1727954263\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clean the mess, install new windows and lights, replace the interior, paint walls, add new furniture and decorative items. Spray paint the outside and prepare for the summer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362620/extras/rv-gif-8.gif?t=1727954263\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1362620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727954263","background_raw"